Package org.thymeleaf.templateresolver

Interface Summary
ITemplateResolutionValidity Common interface for all objects defining the validity of a template resolution.
ITemplateResolver Interface for all Template Resolvers.
 

Class Summary
AbstractTemplateResolver Convenience base class for all Template Resolvers.
AlwaysValidTemplateResolutionValidity Simple implementation of ITemplateResolutionValidity that considers the template resolution to be always cacheable and always valid.
ClassLoaderTemplateResolver Implementation of ITemplateResolver that extends TemplateResolver and uses a ClassLoaderResourceResolver for resource resolution.
FileTemplateResolver Implementation of ITemplateResolver that extends TemplateResolver and uses a FileResourceResolver for resource resolution.
NonCacheableTemplateResolutionValidity Simple implementation of ITemplateResolutionValidity that considers the template resolution to be non-cacheable.
ServletContextTemplateResolver Implementation of ITemplateResolver that extends TemplateResolver and uses a ServletContextResourceResolver for resource resolution.
TemplateResolution Result of the execution of a Template Resolver.
TemplateResolver Basic implementation of ITemplateResolver.
TTLTemplateResolutionValidity Simple implementation of ITemplateResolutionValidity that uses a TTL (time-to-live) expressed in milliseconds to compute the validity of template cache entries.
UrlTemplateResolver Implementation of ITemplateResolver that extends TemplateResolver and uses a UrlResourceResolver for resource resolution.
